src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Midday' game
04 Nov 2019, 18:04 by The Associated Press
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday afternoon's drawing of the Ohio Lottery's "Pick 3 Midday" game were:
5-9-7
(five, nine, seven)
